          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1606140093451-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1606140093451-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1606140093451-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a tray with<strong> tin foil</strong> and add the<strong> halved sprouts</strong>, <strong>red onion wedges</strong> and <strong>butternut squash cubes</strong></p><p>Drizzle with<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give it a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 10 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606140099545-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606140099545-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606140099545-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606140099545-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606140099545-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a dry, medium-sized pot (with a matching lid) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk so you don't burn them!</p><p>Transfer the <strong>toasted almonds</strong> to a plate and reserve the pot</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1606140105419-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1606140105419-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1606140105419-x700.jpg",
