            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>juice </strong>of <strong>1/2</strong> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong> lemon </strong>and the <strong>oregano</strong> with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> on a plate</p><p>Add the<strong> chicken breasts</strong> and toss until coated</p><p>Add the <strong>coated chicken breasts</strong> to the tray, over the<strong> roasting vegetables </strong>and drizzle over the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon and herb marinade</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a further 10 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
